OL,6,FAll 23 people on the tanker were
OL,7,Frescued along with 13 crew from the
OL,8,FSolong, but Mark Angelo Pernia ` a 38-
OL,9,Fyear-old Filipino ` is missing
OL,10,Fpresumed dead.
OL,12,FHe was working in the forward deck
OL,13,Fpart of the Solong, in an area where
OL,14,Fan explosion took place.
OL,16,FThe Solong's master, Vladimir Motin,
OL,17,F59, of Primorsky, St Petersburg, is
OL,18,Fcharged with gross negligence
OL,19,Fmanslaughter. He appeared by video
OL,20,Flink at the Old Bailey for an hour-
OL,21,Flong bail hearing on Friday, 21 March.
