OL,3,CRussian captain of North Sea crash
OL,4,Cship given trial date
OL,6,FMotin, who is married and has a
OL,7,Fdaughter, only spoke to confirm his
OL,8,Fname and date of birth, and had the
OL,9,Fhelp of a Russian interpreter.
OL,11,FNo pleas were entered and he was
OL,12,Fremanded in custody.
OL,14,FJudge Mark Lucraft KC said Motin will
OL,15,Fnext appear for a preliminary hearing
OL,16,Fat the same court on 14 April.
